author: bainbrid
body:
This PR adds the following weights file, on the master branch for the 12_0_X release cycle:
- `LowPtElectrons_ID_2021May17.root`

The 2021May17 file is enabled by the bParking modifier, to used during the UL RE-RECO of the BParking data set, as required by the PR cms-sw/cmssw#33725

The model performances can be found in [this](https://indico.cern.ch/event/1034467/contributions/4344267/attachments/2248230/3813485/LowPtElectrons_PPDMay21.pdf) presentation.
title: LowPtElectrons: 2021May17 model for 12_0_X
